# 🗓️ Multi-Agent Event Planner

An AI-powered **multi-agent event planning system** built with [CrewAI](https://github.com/joaomdmoura/crewai) and [Streamlit](https://streamlit.io/). This application demonstrates how specialized AI agents can collaborate to plan, manage, and review events with structured workflows and user feedback.

<div align="center">
  <img src="images/demo_screenshot.png" width="80%" alt="App Demo Screenshot">
</div>

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🤖 **Multi-Agent Workflow**: Agents work together to plan, review, and refine event details.  
- ✨ **Feedback Loop**: Users can provide feedback during execution, integrated into CrewAI’s flow.  
- 🧠 **Memory-Enabled Agents**: Agents share context for consistency across tasks.  
- 🧩 **Modular System**: Easily extend with new agents, tasks, or tools.  
- 🎯 **Practical Use-Case**: From conferences to parties, the planner provides structured recommendations.  

---

## 🏗️ Architecture Overview

### 🧠 Agents
- **Event Planner Agent** – Creates a detailed event plan based on user input.  
- **Event Reviewer Agent** – Reviews, improves, and finalizes the event plan with refinements.  

### 📋 Tasks
1. **Plan Creation** – Generates an initial draft of the event plan.  
2. **Plan Review** – Evaluates the draft for clarity, feasibility, and improvements.  
3. **Feedback Incorporation** – Integrates user feedback into the final plan.  

### 🛠️ Tools Used
- **Streamlit UI** – Interactive frontend for inputs and feedback.  
- **CrewAI Engine** – Multi-agent orchestration framework.  
- **Custom Input Patching** – Ensures seamless user feedback handling inside Hugging Face Spaces and Streamlit.  

